Instance Methods

moveTarget(newDepth : Int, ?newList : IEditableList<DataType>) : Void

Method wil move the target to the given depth in the given list. If the list is null, then the current list value will be used.

removeTarget() : Void

Method will remove the target from the original list

restore() : Void

Method will put the target on it's old position in the list
